目前已有863箱流入市面，至於該流動攤商剩餘的貨品及津南區庫存的564箱已被封存並進行追蹤，同時全面消毒環境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=893219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D893219&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d2ad91b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D893219&h=33524477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=893219</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"果然強,剩係強國可以係食物度驗到病毒.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467c382c28eb73d7bfa8c092cb30822e1be6ce77","tid":2394564,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"中國獨有 , 封關都有確診唯有賴入口貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e462eec340b551a26acfdf1a2e918b311830563e","tid":2394564,"uid":38703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cb062ada105df716be5121850f82aaebef8b91ba","tid":2394564,"uid":271894,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"全<br />\n全世界剩係得支那先驗到貨物有病毒<br />\n全世界剩係得香港先驗到寵物有病毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"寵物好似其他國家有驗到有病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd380abbb473aa6b8ced3b05c324ebe37d5070d9","tid":2394564,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"進口貨乜閪都話有 流出又唔見你班支支中<br />\n乜都有係支那人無毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18be7550672ad1d3b36cf7dcddf7b67e2745a660","tid":2394564,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0e54f2030d2f6630787a7249ebf95015c42dc99","tid":2394564,"uid":161945,"lik